Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:55.13,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(80,200)}那飽含思念的文字隨風搖曳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:02:00.64,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}あなたには 届かなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:02:00.64,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}卻無法傳到你的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:06.48,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}宇宙を舞い星になる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:06.48,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}飛舞在宇宙 化作繁星點點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:12.36,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}光が切ないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:12.36,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}光芒一明一滅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:18.24,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}踏み締めた足元
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:18.24,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}向前邁出腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:24.12,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}揺らいでしまうから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:24.12,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}卻不能穩立於咆哮的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:30.33,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}手を伸ばしてくれたあの頃を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:30.33,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}你向我伸出援手的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:36.63,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}思い出してる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:36.63,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}在思念的深海中蘇醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:44.35,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}キラリ星屑たち 集めてみても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:44.35,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}我嘗試集聚那閃耀的星塵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:50.35,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}涙 ぽろぽろぽろ こぼれて 消え入るそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:50.35,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}但淚水撲簌而下 消失其間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:56.03,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}ぎゅっと指の隙間 胸に当てたの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:56.03,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}緊握的手指之間 是我熾熱的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:03:03.12,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}何時か 砕け散った約束を リングに変える
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:03:03.12,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}終有一天 散碎的約定就是連接你我的絲線
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.17,0:27:07.64,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}目を覚ましたとき いつもの癖で「おはよう」
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.17,0:27:07.64,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}酣夢初醒 一如往常問早安
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.43,0:27:20.99,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}あと何度 同じ泣きそうな顔させるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.43,0:27:20.99,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}曾經幾回 為君而面露哀傷
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.28,0:27:34.88,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}その運命は まるで蛍火のように見えた
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.28,0:27:34.88,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}命若螢火 過眼雲煙轉瞬逝
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.84,0:27:49.48,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}風を泳ぐように 心を揺らすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.84,0:27:49.48,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}心亂情惘 如若遊弋狂風中
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.94,0:28:02.99,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}何度も 何度も 問いかけても
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.94,0:28:02.99,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}曾幾回 曾幾回 尋蹤覓跡
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.20,0:28:10.29,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}鏡に写る日々は 答えくれない
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.20,0:28:10.29,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}杳然無信 鏡中倒影無回音
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.62,0:28:19.88,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}いつかは 消えた未来もう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.62,0:28:19.88,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}斷緣再續 終將有時
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.59,0:28:26.35,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}信じたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.59,0:28:26.35,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}心誠則明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觸碰了這所學校詛咒的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神會被慢慢侵蝕 陷入錯亂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會毫不猶豫對其他人下手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 不過症狀因人而異
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後肉體會像焦炭一樣染成黑色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而靈魂會被困在這所天神小學裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.26,0:00:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這種現象稱為黑化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.71,0:00:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的朋友觸碰了詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.24,0:01:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她為了守護內心而做了激烈的抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後選擇了自盡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.07,0:01:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你朋友一死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這所學校的活人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只剩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.06,0:01:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.24,0:01:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孑然一人到死為止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經回不到原來的世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只能像一起過來的朋友一樣靜靜等待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起？ 繭也在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繭在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繭在哪裡？ 回不去到底是怎麼一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神町奉知報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天神小學屢屢發生的可怕的犯罪事件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾個月來在町內發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「兒童連續失蹤事件」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經有關部門偵查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就以最糟糕的情況草草結束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昭和48年9月18日晚上7點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在校內發現了失蹤兒童的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及一名手持著沾血的剪刀 精神恍惚的教師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此人目前已被逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就是篠崎說過的殺人事件了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們為什麼會在這個天神小學裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神小學應該在很久之前就被拆掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我們穿越到過去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什麼 我都會保護由香的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:04:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:04:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先去找找大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定直美他們也在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香 想去上廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有一個看著能用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香還能忍一會 去找找別的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 我們也會變成那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 一定能回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擔…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森繁！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去剛死沒多久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不管這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我們 好像還有別的學校的學生被傳過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是一些精神嚴重錯亂的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說都沒反應
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯亂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看上去沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不快點的話 我們也會有危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得是 我們分頭去找大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的辦法到時候再說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行 那我去找繭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到人的話就讓他到前面的緊急出口集合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 持田 差點忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有幽靈 你們小心一些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩的幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是案件的受害者 我看到過一次 傷得很重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候幽靈正在襲擊其他學校的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈會襲擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 還有一個跟我們年紀差不多的幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過應該是無害的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別離開我啊 由香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 篠崎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.03,0:07:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭 頭快要炸開了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再呆在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 振作一點 振作點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的臉在報紙裡看到過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸沼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不要和那傢伙對視
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能對視！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道.....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來這！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥和姐姐 你們誰先想死呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先弄死誰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸沼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先弄死姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就先弄死你好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篠崎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸沼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你也有靈媒體質
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你救了我們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這身校服我沒見過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我們一樣也被關在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經死在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來這裡尋找重要的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你是七星同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識那傢伙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女高中生靈能師 冴之木七星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在靈能探討和心靈情報的主頁上非常出名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 七星同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.51,0:09:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在關注你的網站
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從「幸福的幸子」那個帖子之後就再也沒有更新 我一直很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到居然發生了這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你剛剛說是來這邊找人是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己過來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那既然能來 就肯定有回去的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的話就快點告訴我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸沼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在死去之前 為了逃離而全力調查了這所學校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:10:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過看上去形成這個異空間——天神小學的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那4名連續誘拐殺害事件的受害兒童的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地上報紙裡的那個報導裡的那些小孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的那個也是其中之一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我半途中力竭而倒下 所以沒能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要是能平息那些孩子的靈魂的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許這個空間就會崩壞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們可能就會不再虐待我們 把我們放出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓靈魂平息這種事情要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先兇手的懺悔是必須的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個兇手也在這個學校裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懺悔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對那樣的傢伙我和篠崎又能做…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持田也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友也在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才進來的靈魂有9個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9個 大家都在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就趕快去找他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能找得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:10:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.21,0:11:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是可怕的詛咒形成的多重閉鎖空間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多重閉鎖空間？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在同一個地點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不在一個次元就絕對見不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果是你的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義雄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個教室是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理科教室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兒童的死因是被被捕教室用大裁縫剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪掉舌頭失血過多或者窒息而死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇害兒童中 有一人在死後被切掉頭部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喪心病狂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴本同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴本同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些小孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 她就是我最喜歡的結衣老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也很喜歡學校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴..鈴本同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.05,0:12:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也很喜歡老師 跟你們一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴本同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離那些小孩遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們兩個都不是壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很可憐的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個老師也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 我無法放下這些孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我會留在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 鈴本同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:12:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕緊出去和大家會合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森繁同學也在為你擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 快點一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴本同學是我可愛的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 求求你們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴本同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴本…同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我重要的…學生…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒能保護好她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪啊 繭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若不陪在我身邊 就讓我心如刀絞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我一直這麼想 但這不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.55,0:14:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繭…你的容顏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你喊我繁哥哥的聲音讓我得到的救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繭 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別扔下我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 不看看別人的不幸就不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我過得還算不錯 還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 嘿嘿 收集了好多屍體的照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議 明明都是真的 看上去卻很假
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然這個才是最華麗的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這堆肉醬真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也曾是活生生的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 現在不是做這種事情的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有來電顯示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不要看…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像能聽到什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不要看我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看我 不要看我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看我的內臟…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也沒法用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…就是森繁說的幽靈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看上去沒有受傷的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也在這裡迷路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 她說讓我們過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼小的孩子也被困在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個門外面有什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才過來的時候這邊應該沒有門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香快憋不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在這裡解決嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:16:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有欄杆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這種高度應該沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香 千萬不要接近樹林
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.27,0:17:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 你能陪我一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先進去等你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事了大聲喊我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白檀高等學校 刻命裕也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 森繁也說過這裡有其他學校的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也和我們一樣做了幸子的咒語嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.07,0:17:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:17:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不開 為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 你在哪裡？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回一聲啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在多重閉鎖空間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們或許無法見面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果持田他們能夠看見這個蠟燭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就可能告訴他我們也在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 義雄就是那個兇手教師的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人偶可能就是那個兇手的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是要我們通過人偶來獲得兇手的懺悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這人偶長得真滲人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺隨時都會開口說話 真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對..不..起..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人..人偶說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 岸沼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了那麼多孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的精神出了問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有打算殺他們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.43,0:19:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 岸沼..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音能當做兇手的懺悔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是裝在袋子的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.21,0:19:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.18,0:19:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉澤遼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得遇害兒童裡面有個叫這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我看看..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 吉澤遼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是剛才襲擊我們的小鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}還給我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又蹦出來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是吉澤遼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.89,0:20:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的…還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是說「還給我」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的舌頭...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那樣算是平息了那個小鬼的靈魂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸沼你拿到的是那個孩子被兇手切掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舌頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 還有三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須找到他們的舌頭還給他們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點的話 人偶還會告訴我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:54.12,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(28.667,32.667)}管乃雪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:54.12,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(151.333,59.333)}辻時子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:54.12,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(28,90)}吉澤遼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篠崎你真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不怕那些幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.47,0:21:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是強裝鎮定而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是怪某些人靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.79,0:22:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好..好了 就剩一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.48,0:22:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得名字叫篠崎幸子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.46,0:22:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是沒錯……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.96,0:22:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是根據報導
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.88,0:22:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸子應該在遭到殺害之前就被發現了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.51,0:22:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕用對付遼的辦法是無法讓她平息的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.46,0:22:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平息什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子不是沒事麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.17,0:22:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她就應該好好活著 變成老太婆了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.23,0:22:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 所有的孩子都得到平息了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.72,0:22:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是什麼都沒有發生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.13,0:22:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 原來是鐘聲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人嚇一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.62,0:22:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之這算是告一段落了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.91,0:22:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得還有什麼重要的事情還沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.74,0:23:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.39,0:23:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.57,0:23:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.13,0:23:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是持田的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.97,0:23:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 腦袋變得好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.64,0:23:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都是這樣的屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.95,0:23:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持田呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥...哥哥 不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你在瑟瑟發抖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.63,0:23:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來吧 我跟你一起找
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.93,0:23:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香自己去找...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.66,0:23:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說幫你去找你哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.93,0:23:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但...但是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這孩子真不懂事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.22,0:23:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧了 我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.30,0:23:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.06,0:24:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.24,0:24:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別躲著了 快出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.94,0:24:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有事跟你說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.11,0:24:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那個時候跟繭也約好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.86,0:24:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好了要永遠在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.06,0:24:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你也變成繭那樣讓我收在手機裡面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.05,0:24:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 繭子就不會寂寞了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.77,0:24:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡 你快出來吧 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.96,0:24:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.44,0:24:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方捉迷藏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.96,0:24:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛在說「哥哥」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.44,0:24:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我和哥哥走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.15,0:24:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.53,0:24:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也在找妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.33,0:24:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話 我們一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.96,0:25:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是白檀高等學校二年級的刻命裕也
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.85,0:25:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是持田由香
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.03,0:25:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是因為幸子的咒語被困在這裡了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.21,0:25:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 那個 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.99,0:25:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.00,0:25:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.30,0:25:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到我這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.38,0:25:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不認識他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.80,0:25:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.14,0:25:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.27,0:25:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以剛才才躲起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.66,0:25:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.35,0:25:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要來手機裡陪繭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.61,0:25:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.64,0:25:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香你待在這
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.20,0:26:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.55,0:26:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你可是我最重要的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.30,0:26:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
